{{Noticebox/Community}}

'''Leaks''' are potential unreleased or unannounced features or information found through various credible or non-credible means, such as the [[VRChat API]] or platforms like Crowdin. Anything on this page should be taken with a grain of salt; just because something is on this page, does not confirm that it is something that will be added in the future.

Leaks will typically be removed from this page when they are either confirmed (through being given an applicable testing branch on [[Open Beta]], or being fully released) then after [[VRCWiki:How to Contribute|receiving an article]] on the [[VRCWiki:About|VRChat Wiki]], or assigned within the proper existing articles; or removed after being denied through official VRChat sources.

== Events ==

===Holiday Event<ref>`Holiday Event` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139197 Crowdin]</ref>===
By gifting VRC+ or from the Shop (Exclusive, Avatars, World stores), users will be able to earn personal rewards such as a warp effect (gift 5 VRC+), premium emojis, stickers, a portal (gift 1 VRC+) and a badge once the corresponding goals have been reached.<ref>`Gift a VRC+ subscription to unlock an exclusive holiday Portal.` `Campaign call to action for the VRC+ gifter reward` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139231 Crowdin]</ref><ref>`Send 5 VRC+ or Shop gifts (Exclusive, Avatars, World stores) to claim this festive Warp Effect.` `Campaign call to action for the Holiday Legend reward` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139237 Crowdin]</ref><ref>`Send any VRC+ or Shop gift (Exclusive, Avatars, World stores) to earn an exclusive Premium Emoji.` `Campaign reward call to action for the first gift` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139225 Crowdin]</ref> Rewards are shared on a friends and global leaderboard ordered by top "givers"<ref>`You've opted out of the Top Givers list.` `Confirmation message when a user has chosen to appear as anonymous on the leaderboard` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139219 Crowdin]</ref> which are called "2025 Holiday Heroes"<ref>`2025 Holiday Heroes` `Message at the top of the leaderboard` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139223 Crowdin]</ref>, you can appear as anonymous on global leaderboard.<ref>`Appear as Anonymous` `Button to make yourself anonymous on the leaderboards` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139255 Crowdin]</ref>
Starting date TBA, ends the 31st of December. 

Bundles:
* Festive Starter Pack <ref>`Festive Starter Pack` `Campaign reward title message for the` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139255 Crowdin]</ref>

Campaign rewards:
