* Holiday Legend<ref>`Holiday Legend` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139241 Crowdin]</ref>
* VRC+ Gifter<ref>`VRC+ Gifter` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139235 Crowdin]</ref>
* Community Spirit Reward<ref>`Community Spirit Reward` - [https://crowdin.com/editor/vrchat-application/19#139247 Crowdin]</ref>

